<p>A paragraph is a series of related sentences developing a central idea, called the topic. </p>
<p>Try to think about paragraphs in terms of thematic unity:
a paragraph is a sentence or a group of sentences that supports one central, unified idea.</p>
<p> Paragraphs add one idea at a time to your broader argument.</p>
